org.sampleapp.dto

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sampleapp.dto.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    The User Class holds together all the members of a WAAD User entity and all the access methods and set methods to access or set any particular member attribute of such an object instance.
